episodes.title: The Pee Pee Guy
episodes.plot: A business associate falls from grace, while Ray takes the fall for a mate. A chance meeting in the park and a new apprentice.

episodes.title: Unicorns Know Everybody's Name
episodes.plot: The wrong guy gets the good news and Unicorn's do exist. The first of a thousand kisses and good ole revenge.

episodes.title: Captain Obvious
episodes.plot: Anger mismanagement and no such thing as Jesus. If you can't kill your own brother-in-law, who can?

episodes.title: On Behalf of Society
episodes.plot: Ray doesn't like surprises, sit downs, sandwiches, or assholes. Brittany asks tough questions, while Ray hands out trouble to those that seek it.

episodes.title: Hard Worker
episodes.plot: People are not always what they appear to be and a good strong name is important. It's also important to lock your car when you leave it.

episodes.title: Your Mum's Got a Strongbox
episodes.plot: A nutritious breakfast is the key to good health. As is looking in the trunk before stealing a car. People say they do but does anybody really like surprises?
